query:
INSERT INTO structure
            (
                owner,
                structure_id,
                system_id,
                type_id,
                rigs,
                services,
                name,
                x,
                y,
                z
            )
            SELECT
                $1 AS owner,
                s.structure_id,
                s.system_id,
                s.type_id,
                s.rigs,
                s.services,
                s.name,
                s.x,
                s.y,
                s.z
            FROM industry_hub_structure ihs
            JOIN structure s ON ihs.structure_id = s.id
            WHERE ihs.industry_hub_id = $2
            RETURNING id
